text.__SUMMARY__: Zamia meermanii is a species of cycad in the family Zamiaceae endemic to central Belize. It is found on limestone cliffs.
text.References: Whitelock, Loran M. 2002. The Cycads. Portland: Timber Press. ISBN 0-88192-522-5
